{"tid":188554,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[健康台]有無人背脊舊骨會凸左出嚟？","createTime":"2017-04-05T18:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T19:04:34.000Z","uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"54cc202d8fbd330a7348e80e7112f0bd695ed9ec","tid":188554,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T18:01:11.000Z","msg":"細細個打機坐姿唔好 成日&ldquo;挨&ldquo;埋右邊咁打機<br />\n大個左發現右邊背骨凸左出嚟 搞到成日都好唔自在好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時要整到舊骨啪左一聲先舒服一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲有同樣經歷？可以點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個病跟左幾年 我見無乜大問題一直無理 其實係咪應該睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51db63272a979bf08321d30e1f97966562798b46","tid":188554,"uid":30686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T18:07:54.000Z","msg":"椎間盤突入冇得醫<br />\n手術可以搞<br />\n<br />\n利申，我都有，但輕微<br />\n依加努力調整緊姿勢"},{"pid":"60c5c4b334d1336f6f7729d5041b5481d551ea11","tid":188554,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T18:15:10.000Z","msg":"有 不過我係太瘦 近尾龍骨果到一彎腰就係排骨露得好勁"},{"pid":"2cc5c1c7dfd83540e53925e86c4ff6f90a3a26ac","tid":188554,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T18:15:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>椎間盤突入冇得醫<br />\n手術可以搞<br />\n<br />\n利申，我都有，但輕微<br />\n依加努力調整緊姿勢</blockquote><br />\n點調整法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盡量坐直？另外雖然無得醫 但有無方法改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉筋有無得諗"},{"pid":"d05b1a2772412f568df29c04b773a5bc535070da","tid":188554,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T18:20:29.000Z","msg":"我都係&hellip;<br />\n啲人話老咗就好辛苦&hellip;"},{"pid":"59ffcf3c859c23a51f42d559887d7c7c503c392a","tid":188554,"uid":49124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T18:20:4